
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google reviews (Google Places API — New)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The testimonials sections pull live reviews from the GROUTIX Google Business
# Profile. If these are left blank, the site falls back to curated reviews.
#
# Setup:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/ and create (or pick) a project.
# 2. APIs & Services → Library → enable "Places API (New)".
# 3. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create credentials → API key.
#    Restrict it to the "Places API (New)" and (recommended) to your server IP.
# 4. Find your Place ID with https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/places/web-service/place-id
#    (search your business name; copy the "Place ID" string, e.g. ChIJ...).
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=AIzaSyAuP7kswkFDeHgJPOl8shofwL8E4vhDywQ
GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=ChIJ2UgwstzRPUkRDCsaRuYN4KI
